Chinese designers have developed a washing machine so cyclists can clean clothes while exercising  . 
  A generator inside the bike also creates electricity which can be stored for future use . 
  The Bike Washing Machine contains a machine drum in its front wheel . 
  When ridden, the pedalling motion causes the drum to rotate . 
  Designers at Dalian Nationalities University say the device is perfect for those struggling to find space for both . 
 